extendedInfo.description: Stay connected with City & County Credit Union's FREE mobile app - a fast and secure way to manage your accounts.  Easily check balances, view account activity, pay bills, deposit checks, make transfers, or find the nearest City & County location or ATMs.

reviews.title: Simple, overall good
reviews.comment: It would great if we could take this app to the next level. Allow me to add/modify payees in the bill payer, schedule transfers, some of the functions allowed on the website.  CCCU is the best. I have been banking with them since I was 12. I tried TCF once for about 30 days and got so mad on how I was treated I will never go back. They get almost every loan from me and all savings.
reviews.author: Ben Granley

reviews.title: Would be great if it worked right
